body.raw: David Wilson is a dedicated immigration attorney committed to assisting individuals and families navigate the complex immigration process. Born to immigrant parents, David understands the challenges immigrants face firsthand. He earned his law degree from Columbia Law School and has since advocated for immigrant rights, providing compassionate legal representation and fighting against unjust immigration policies.
